### FoodApp AI Assistant Chat
# The AI is configured as a helpful assistant that can search for products and check order details.

### 1. General Product Inquiry
# Ask the AI to list available products. 
# It will use the 'searchProducts' tool and then summarize the results.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi, what products do you have? I'm looking for some drinks."
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Search for Specific Products
# Search for products by name or category.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Do you have any coffee? Maybe a Latte?"
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Get Detailed Product Information
# Ask for details about a specific product using its slug.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Can you tell me more about the 'yogurt-trai-cay'?"
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Check Order Status
# Track an order by its unique code.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi, can you check the status of my order VD-DE-1780747990298"
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Multi-turn Conversation
# The AI maintains context if you pass the message history.
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What coffee do you have?"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "We have several coffee options including Espresso, Americano, Cappuccino, Latte, Mocha, and Cold Brew. Which one would you like to know more about?"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Tell me about the Cold Brew price and description."
    }
  ]
}
